    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to be posting this, but it\u2019s time for this absolute beauty to find a new home. If you\u2019re like me and appreciate a car that\u2019s been pampered since day one, you\u2019re going to love this. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still has that fresh feel every time you hop inside. I\u2019ve spent more weekends than I can count polishing it and making sure every detail is just right. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself how special this one is!",
