    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa. This S54 powerplant is a masterclass in atmospheric induction, featuring a fully overhauled Double VANOS system and treated rod bearings for absolute peace of mind at the 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is laser-straight, benefiting from proactive subframe reinforcement and a precision-tuned suspension geometry featuring Bilstein PSS10 damping. Power delivery is immediate through the 6-speed Getrag box and a recalibrated M-Variable differential. Every bushing has been refreshed to polyurethane for tactile feedback, ensuring this chassis remains composed under high lateral G-loads. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically optimized instrument of precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
