      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this truly exceptional specimen. Maintained to the highest standards, this vehicle presents in showroom condition, boasting an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory freshness. Every detail, from the precision-tuned mechanicals to the pristine upholstery, reflects a legacy of meticulous care. This is more than a pre-owned car; it is an investment in quality and performance for those who refuse to compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
