    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this absolute gem go, but it's time for someone else to experience the joy it brings. I\u2019ve treated this beauty like a member of the family\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single Sunday. It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape, looking just as fresh as the day it rolled off the lot. You won\u2019t find a single hair out of place here! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with every mile, come by and take a look. I'd love to chat cars and show you why this one is so special.",
      "price": 48500.0,
