    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade E92 M3, meticulously curated for the discerning purist. This S65-powered masterpiece features a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band that screams to its 8,400 RPM redline. I\u2019ve performed extensive preventative maintenance, including VAC coated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure peak structural integrity. The DCT software has been optimized for lightning-fast shifts, while the EDC suspension maintains perfect damping geometry. Wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on unblemished ZCP wheels, the turn-in bite and lateral grip are unparalleled. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing zero signs of thermal cycling stress or track fatigue. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a high-compression symphony of German engineering in absolute concours condition.",
